        <num>40-13-25</num>
        <content>
          <p>The costs in any case disposed of under this article shall be as provided in Code Section 15-9-60. In case a defendant refuses to waive a trial by jury and is bound over to another court, the costs shall await the final disposition of the case.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1937-38, Ex. Sess., p. 558, ยง 5.)</p>
